{"tid":2222934,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"台灣立委提修例防中資全方位滲透 影響台灣政局穩定","createTime":"2020-09-29T12:09:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-29T12:21:43.000Z","uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"12af50ead9d83355fc81a58e0d9651d7f743ff3e","tid":2222934,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T12:09:09.000Z","msg":"在周二（29日）的聯合舉行記者會中，經民連智庫召集人賴中強表示，現行用來規範中資行為的「兩岸人民關係條例」，是在2002年制定非常古老的條文，20年來中國不斷進行資本擴張，全球經濟情勢已有重大轉變。中資與港資、外資的界線已經越來越模糊，如果台灣的法規持續認定港資並非中資，恐怕國家安全、經濟安全與社會安定都會受到衝擊。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/htm/tw-law-09292020075147.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fcantonese%2Fnews%2Fhtm%2Ftw-law-09292020075147.html&d=3%2F9Bgz%2Fikyxb3M9FpachXNTLU9NF7cMiG%2FeCYohcYb8%3D&h=b88efb28\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/htm/tw-law-09292020075147.html</a>"},{"pid":"09049c62c07db2186a26222bb1209f218f29c5de","tid":2222934,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T12:21:43.000Z","msg":"大家簽左有法律效力嘅德國聯署未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n「簽乜撚聯署啊？都無用嘅 不如放棄啦」<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2222912\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2222912</a>"}]}